snippet.title: Reignbreaker | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Reignbreaker is a single-player medievalpunk roguelike coming to PC. Smash the kingdom, take back their hoarded wealth, and try again & again until the queen is dead.

►Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2129810/
►Join our newsletter: http://playreignbreaker.com/

Developed by Studio Fizbin
Published by Thunderful
